Maaari akong magpatotoo.

00:36:24.980 --> 00:36:26.190
Narinig ko gamit ang sarili kong mga tainga

00:36:26.190 --> 00:36:27.030
Bai Yingsheng at Jiang Yiqian's

00:36:27.030 --> 00:36:27.760
sabwatan.

